    {
      "para_id": "p1",
      "section_id": "s1",
      "section_path": [
        "Summary of UNA Associates' Responses to the Public Consultation on the Digital Fairness Act"
      ],
      "ordinal": 1,
      "text": "The responses collected from UNA's associates provide a detailed overview of the challenges and concerns experienced by consumers and businesses in the digital environment. These insights are drawn directly from the consultation document.",
      "char_len": 238,
      "chunk_word_count": 33,
      "ratios": {
        "alpha": 0.9854368932038835,
        "digit": 0.0,
        "non_space": 0.865546218487395
      },
      "meaning": {
        "score": 0.7599110032362459,
        "flags": []
      },
      "selection": {
        "selected": true,
        "policy": "threshold+top_k"
      },
      "chunk_quality": "ok"
    },
    {
      "para_id": "p2",
      "section_id": "s2",
      "section_path": [
        "Summary of UNA Associates' Responses to the Public Consultation on the Digital Fairness Act",
        "1. Principal Challenges for Consumers"
      ],
      "ordinal": 2,
      "text": "UNA's associates report a variety of recurring challenges:",
      "char_len": 58,
      "chunk_word_count": 8,
      "ratios": {
        "alpha": 0.9607843137254902,
        "digit": 0.0,
        "non_space": 0.8793103448275862
      },
      "meaning": {
        "score": 0.42058823529411765,
        "flags": [
          "very_short"
        ]
      },
      "selection": {
        "selected": true,
        "policy": "top_k"
      },
      "chunk_quality": "ok"
    },
    {
      "para_id": "p3",
      "section_id": "s2",
      "section_path": [
        "Summary of UNA Associates' Responses to the Public Consultation on the Digital Fairness Act",
        "1. Principal Challenges for Consumers"
      ],
      "ordinal": 3,
      "text": "Market and Data Practices: Respondents noted some concerns regarding the widespread presence of online advertising, privacy-related profiling, and the ways in which data is collected and used, which are at times perceived as not fully transparent. There is also an observed trend towards the increased use of user-generated content and personal data for automated and AI-driven processes, with room for improvement in how such practices are communicated to users.",
      "char_len": 463,
      "chunk_word_count": 69,
      "ratios": {
        "alpha": 0.9746835443037974,
        "digit": 0.0,
        "non_space": 0.8531317494600432
      },
      "meaning": {
        "score": 0.9810126582278481,
        "flags": []
      },
      "selection": {
        "selected": true,
        "policy": "threshold+top_k"
      },
      "chunk_quality": "ok"
    },
    {
      "para_id": "p4",
      "section_id": "s2",
      "section_path": [
        "Summary of UNA Associates' Responses to the Public Consultation on the Digital Fairness Act",
        "1. Principal Challenges for Consumers"
      ],
      "ordinal": 4,
      "text": "Targeted advertising, when implemented responsibly, can serve as an effective means of providing users with information, products, and services that are relevant to their needs and interests, often aligning with what they are actively seeking. Ensuring transparency in the criteria used for personalization, safeguarding sensitive data, and strictly prohibiting the targeting of minors are essential measures. Combined with these protections, targeted marketing can deliver safe and meaningful content while respecting individual rights.",
      "char_len": 537,
      "chunk_word_count": 72,
      "ratios": {
        "alpha": 0.9763948497854077,
        "digit": 0.0,
        "non_space": 0.8677839851024208
      },
      "meaning": {
        "score": 0.9822961373390557,
        "flags": []
      },
      "selection": {
        "selected": true,
        "policy": "threshold+top_k"
      },
      "chunk_quality": "ok"
    },
    {
      "para_id": "p5",
      "section_id": "s2",
      "section_path": [
        "Summary of UNA Associates' Responses to the Public Consultation on the Digital Fairness Act",
        "1. Principal Challenges for Consumers"
      ],
      "ordinal": 5,
      "text": "Lack of Transparency and Comprehension: Contracts and terms of service are often lengthy, complex, and difficult to interpret, with key information about sales conditions in e-commerce sometimes presented in ways that are not immediately clear.",
      "char_len": 244,
      "chunk_word_count": 35,
      "ratios": {
        "alpha": 0.9714285714285714,
        "digit": 0.0,
        "non_space": 0.860655737704918
      },
      "meaning": {
        "score": 0.7799603174603175,
        "flags": []
      },
      "selection": {
        "selected": true,
        "policy": "threshold+top_k"
      },
      "chunk_quality": "ok"
    },
    {
      "para_id": "p6",
      "section_id": "s2",
      "section_path": [
        "Summary of UNA Associates' Responses to the Public Consultation on the Digital Fairness Act",
        "1. Principal Challenges for Consumers"
      ],
      "ordinal": 6,
      "text": "Misleading or Low-Quality Content: Examples include AI-generated images that may be perceived as deceptive, the sale of products of inconsistent quality, violent or harmful material, fake reviews, and undeclared commercial partnerships.",
      "char_len": 236,
      "chunk_word_count": 31,
      "ratios": {
        "alpha": 0.9611650485436893,
        "digit": 0.0,
        "non_space": 0.8728813559322034
      },
      "meaning": {
        "score": 0.7111515641855448,
        "flags": []
      },
      "selection": {
        "selected": true,
        "policy": "threshold+top_k"
      },
      "chunk_quality": "ok"
    },
    {
      "para_id": "p7",
      "section_id": "s2",
      "section_path": [
        "Summary of UNA Associates' Responses to the Public Consultation on the Digital Fairness Act",
        "1. Principal Challenges for Consumers"
      ],
      "ordinal": 7,
      "text": "Insufficient Digital Literacy: Limited awareness of privacy rights and the value of personal data, coupled with superficial engagement with digital services.",
      "char_len": 157,
      "chunk_word_count": 21,
      "ratios": {
        "alpha": 0.9781021897810219,
        "digit": 0.0,
        "non_space": 0.8726114649681529
