    {
      "para_id": "p47",
      "section_id": "s14",
      "section_path": [
        "8. Urgent Measures for Digital Fairness",
        "Conclusion and Key Takeaways"
      ],
      "ordinal": 47,
      "text": "The consultation responses from UNA’s associates highlight the need for a Digital Fairness Act that addresses consumer challenges in the digital environment through clear, enforceable, and harmonized EU regulations. Certain aspects of this regulation may have significant effects on all sides of the supply chain, potentially even resulting in harm to the public itself it aims to safeguard.",
